Patch Set 1:

The questions now are: why did it work ~20 days ago? Are other branches affected?

Patch Set 1:

> The questions now are: why did it work ~20 days ago? Are other
 > branches affected?

No Idea, It is not failing on master branch and failing consistently on stable/stein branch. So far we are not able to figure out the reason behind this error, but due to length of log size this error occurs. Not sure why it was working 20 days ago and not now.

Patch Set 1:

The difference was that functional was using python2, and now it's using python3 (3.6). But the base functional for this version should still be using python 2.7, afaik. The switch happened later.
